  "body": "- Make `mode` undefined in `BrandingProvider` as this case is handled in the component\r\n- Remove no longer used `@mui/docs` re-exports from `docs/src/*`\r\n  - https://github.com/mui/mui-x/pull/13713 and https://github.com/mui/mui-toolpad/pull/3751 ditches last remaining usages\r\n  - Update imports of usages in the codebase to rely on direct imports from `@mui/docs`\r\n- Use `MarkdownElement` from `@mui/docs` instead of the re-export",
